name: RangeHyperlink
description: Represents the necessary strings to getset a hyperlink (XHL) object.

properties.name: screenTip
properties.description: Represents the string displayed when hovering over the hyperlink.

properties.name: address
properties.description: Represents the url target for the hyperlink.

properties.name: documentReference
properties.description: Represents the document reference target for the hyperlink.

properties.name: textToDisplay
properties.description: Represents the string that is displayed in the top left most cell in the range.
